      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "Arbor 0.2.0 focuses on reliable structure recovery and a cleaner opening flow.\n\n- Notes now store precise visible block markers while keeping hidden Arbor metadata.\n- Legacy Arbor notes upgrade automatically to the new format when opened.\n- Managed notes open through a dedicated Arbor loading view instead of flashing the standard markdown view.\n- Auto-open rules are stricter, so marker-like snippets in normal notes are no longer hijacked.\n- Added `New arbor note`, predictable untitled numbering, and improved main-pane opening behavior.\r\n",
